  <div class="about-content">
    <p>
      Hello! I'm a passionate professional with expertise in my field. I have
      several years of experience working on various projects and initiatives.
    </p>
    <p>
      My background includes education in relevant subjects and continuous
      learning to stay updated with the latest developments in my industry.
